    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. Relative hemolysis index predictions are within the 20% validation tolerance band, and the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met across all 5 operating conditions evaluated.",
